            <lg xml:id="TK443">
<l>ariyavaṟṟu ḷellā maritē periyāraip</l>
<l>pēṇit tamarāk koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To cherish great men and make them his own, is the most difficult of all difficult things.</l>
            </lg>
